<!--  INTRODUCTION  -->
<p>
<b>PREP:</b> 30 min; <b>Cooking time:</b> 1&frac14; hr
</p>

<p>
Serves 8
<br />
<br />
<i>This is the New England (white) clam chowder, made with milk. All chowders are made with pork, usually bacon. You can make this without any pork at all. It is delicious either way.
</i>
</p>

